        "created_at": "2019-07-23T11:38:09.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Same here on the 2009. It\u2019s a hard wine. Reminds me of the Burgaud wines, which I stopped buying as they were not what I was looking for in Beaujolais.</p>",
