        "created_at": "2019-07-23T13:33:01.000Z",
        "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-post=\"6\" data-topic=\"153572\">\n<blockquote>\n<p>Same here on the 2009. It\u2019s a hard wine. Reminds me of the Burgaud wines, which I stopped buying as they were not what I was looking for in Beaujolais.</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>Burgaud\u2019s wines have evolved even more than those of the Ch\u00e2teau des Jacques in the last decade! Give his 2018 Beaujolais-Villages a try and see if they still don\u2019t meet your criteria.</p>",
