        "created_at": "2019-07-24T03:52:22.000Z",
        "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-post=\"9\" data-topic=\"153572\">\n<blockquote>\n<p>Drew - why didn\u2019t this go with your fish?</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>Just tuning back in here.  Arv, the salmon was very salmon and it clashed with the tannin.  For a red to work, perhaps one with a bit more glycerin would have been needed.  The fruit was more apparent on its own.</p>",
